ence\": \"It was Jolly's intention to deliver a maximalist display that leaned into French clich\\u00e9s and stereotypes.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9748423321923971, \"rank\": 0.02401027515697016, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jolly's intention\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"a maximalist display\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"stereotypes\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a previousinterview withThe AP, he said, \\\"When we watchEmily in ParisorAm\\u00e9lie Poulain, we know it's not quite the real Paris.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.899220424458661e-15, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 1205, \"end\": 1210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8344717717752378e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a previousinterview\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"ParisorAm\\u00e9lie Poulain\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1171}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to play with all those cliches, but we are also going to challenge them.\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all those cliches\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is also a vibrant youth.\", \"from\"